responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "33E1D6CF4C68FC55B48EB4BE68751404", "I see the ugly, filthy faces of goblins everywhere, not only before my shield but also reflected in my supper soup and in the clouds which drift in my sleep. They lurk at every corner and behind every door. It makes me sick to my stomach to think they will be the final image of this world as I lay dying.")
